Joe Coombs (born 17 March 1991 in Salisbury) is a British canoe slalom athlete who has competed since the age of 12. His results to date include a Silver Medal at the Junior European Championships in 2009 (team-event), 15th at the ICF Senior Pre-world Championships in 2010, and a UK ranking of 5th.

Coombs also competes for Nottingham Trent University and took 3 golds in the 2011 BUCS Canoe Slalom Championships.
